To insert something, you replace a range with the insertion character,

01:04:21.780 --> 01:04:27.260
like a like a new line plus the previous string so everything boils down to like one very simple

01:04:27.480 --> 01:04:33.840
primitive and once you find the right primitive bigger problems become much much easier yeah

01:04:35.360 --> 01:04:43.140
100 it's it's amazing the way it works so we'll get short on time we got pick one more one more

01:04:43.320 --> 01:04:50.160
lesson from here that you want to i want to talk about maybe um the spatial map was quite interesting

